      "duration": 3.04,
      "size": 48672,
      "text": "在老式示波器上，把两个正弦信号分别接到横轴和纵轴，屏幕上会出现优美的花纹。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lissajous",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lissajous/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.34,
      "size": 37440,
      "text": "这些花纹叫做利萨茹图形，是两个垂直方向振动合成的轨迹。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lissajous",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lissajous/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.1,
      "size": 33552,
      "text": "而在极坐标里，一个简单的余弦函数能开出一朵朵玫瑰。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lissajous",
      "section_id": "lissajous",
      "line_id": "lis-3",
      "filename": "lissajous-lis-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lissajous/lissajous-lis-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.44,
      "size": 39024,
      "text": "把频率比改成 3 比 2，曲线开始交错缠绕，形成更复杂的网格。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lissajous",
      "section_id": "lissajous",
      "line_id": "lis-4",
      "filename": "lissajous-lis-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lissajous/lissajous-lis-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.86,
      "size": 29808,
      "text": "只要频率比是简单整数比，图形就会闭合而稳定。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lissajous",
      "section_id": "rose",
      "line_id": "rose-1",
      "filename": "rose-rose-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lissajous/rose-rose-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.38,
      "size": 38016,
      "text": "换到极坐标，半径 r 等于 cos(k 乘以 θ)，就得到玫瑰曲线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lissajous",
      "section_id": "rose",
      "line_id": "rose-2",
      "filename": "rose-rose-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lissajous/rose-rose-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.8,
      "size": 28800,
      "text": "当 k 是奇数，比如 3，玫瑰开出 3 片花瓣。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lissajous",
      "section_id": "why",
      "line_id": "why-1",
      "filename": "why-why-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lissajous/why-why-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.81,
      "size": 28944,
      "text": "这些图形的对称性，来自三角函数本身的周期性。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lissajous",
      "section_id": "why",
      "line_id": "why-2",
      "filename": "why-why-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lissajous/why-why-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.45,
      "size": 39168,
      "text": "频率比和花瓣数，把抽象的数字关系，变成了肉眼可见的几何秩序。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lissajous",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lissajous/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29376,
      "text": "数一数玫瑰曲线的花瓣，验证它和 k 的奇偶关系。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lissajous",
      "section_id": "summary",
